      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8 w-full">
        <div class="max-w-2xl hero-accent-bar">
          <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim tracking-wider mb-8 reveal" style="font-family: var(--font-mono);">
            Full-stack Developer &mdash; Melbourne, AU
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6 reveal reveal-delay-1" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
            I build financial tools<br/>and real-time systems.
